+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                         | 
|  Author:    Karl McMurdo (user xrxca on roundcubeforum.net)             |
|  Plugin:    markbuttons                                                 |
|  Purpose:   Quick Marking Buttons at bottom of Message List             |
|                                                                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+

markbuttons is a Roundcube webmail plugin that adds buttons at the bottom
of the message list to compliment the selection buttons.

Four button are added, Mark as: Read, Unread, Flagged, UnFlagged

Stable releases in TAR format are available under Downloads.

To download the current source in either ZIP or TAR format
click on the 'Download Source' button near the top.

The zip or tar.gz file will have a xrxca-markbuttons-????? directory
that will contain the actual markbuttons plugin directory
move/copy the markbuttons directory to your plugins directory
and enable the plugin in your config/main.inc.php file.

